{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"What I wanted to talk to you about today is two things:"},{"time":3000,"text":"one, the rise of a culture of availability;"},{"time":6000,"text":"and two, a request."},{"time":9000,"text":"So we're seeing a rise of this availability"},{"time":11000,"text":"being driven by mobile device proliferation,"},{"time":14000,"text":"globally, across all social strata."},{"time":16000,"text":"We're seeing, along with that proliferation of mobile devices,"},{"time":19000,"text":"an expectation of availability."},{"time":21000,"text":"And, with that, comes the third point,"},{"time":23000,"text":"which is obligation -- and an obligation to that availability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"And the problem is, we're still working through,"},{"time":29000,"text":"from a societal standpoint,"},{"time":31000,"text":"how we allow people to be available."},{"time":34000,"text":"There's a significant delta, in fact,"},{"time":36000,"text":"between what we're willing to accept."},{"time":38000,"text":"Apologies to Hans Rosling --"},{"time":39000,"text":"he said anything that's not using real stats is a lie --"},{"time":42000,"text":"but the big delta there"},{"time":44000,"text":"is how we deal with this from a public standpoint."},{"time":47000,"text":"So we've developed certain tactics and strategies"},{"time":50000,"text":"to cover up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"This first one's called \"the lean.\""},{"time":54000,"text":"And if you've ever been in a meeting where you play sort of meeting \"chicken,\""},{"time":57000,"text":"you're sitting there, looking at the person, waiting for them to look away,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and then quickly checking the device."},{"time":62000,"text":"Although you can see the gentleman up on the right is busting him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"\"The stretch.\""},{"time":66000,"text":"OK, the gentleman on the left is saying, \"Screw you,"},{"time":69000,"text":"I'm going to check my device.\""},{"time":71000,"text":"But the guy, here, on the right,"},{"time":73000,"text":"he's doing the stretch."},{"time":75000,"text":"It's that reeeee-e-e-each out, the physical contortion"},{"time":77000,"text":"to get that device just below the tabletop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"Or, my favorite, the \"Love you; mean it.\""},{"time":82000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":84000,"text":"Nothing says \"I love you\""},{"time":86000,"text":"like \"Let me find somebody else I give a damn about.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"Or, this one, coming to us from India."},{"time":90000,"text":"You can find this on YouTube,"},{"time":92000,"text":"the gentleman who's recumbent on a motorcycle"},{"time":94000,"text":"while text messaging."},{"time":95000,"text":"Or what we call the \"sweet gravy, stop me before I kill again!\""},{"time":99000,"text":"That is actually the device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"What this is doing is, we find a --"},{"time":104000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":106000,"text":"a direct collision --"},{"time":110000,"text":"we find a direct collision between availability --"},{"time":113000,"text":"and what's possible through availability --"},{"time":116000,"text":"and a fundamental human need -- which we've been hearing about a lot, actually --"},{"time":119000,"text":"the need to create shared narratives."},{"time":123000,"text":"We're very good at creating personal narratives,"},{"time":126000,"text":"but it's the shared narratives that make us a culture."},{"time":129000,"text":"And when you're standing with someone,"},{"time":132000,"text":"and you're on your mobile device,"},{"time":134000,"text":"effectively what you're saying to them is,"},{"time":136000,"text":"\"You are not as important as, literally,"},{"time":139000,"text":"almost anything that could come to me through this device.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"Look around you."},{"time":145000,"text":"There might be somebody on one right now,"},{"time":147000,"text":"participating in multi-dimensional engagement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"Our reality right now is less interesting"},{"time":155000,"text":"than the story we're going to tell about it later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"This one I love."},{"time":160000,"text":"This poor kid, clearly a prop --"},{"time":162000,"text":"don't get me wrong, a willing prop --"},{"time":164000,"text":"but the kiss that's being documented kind of looks like it sucks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"This is the sound of one hand clapping."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"So, as we lose the context of our identity,"},{"time":174000,"text":"it becomes incredibly important"},{"time":177000,"text":"that what you share becomes the context of shared narrative,"},{"time":180000,"text":"becomes the context in which we live."},{"time":182000,"text":"The stories that we tell -- what we push out --"},{"time":185000,"text":"becomes who we are."},{"time":187000,"text":"People aren't simply projecting identity,"},{"time":189000,"text":"they're creating it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"And so that's the request I have for everybody in this room."},{"time":193000,"text":"We are creating the technology"},{"time":194000,"text":"that is going to create the new shared experience,"},{"time":196000,"text":"which will create the new world."},{"time":198000,"text":"And so my request is,"},{"time":200000,"text":"please, let's make technologies"},{"time":202000,"text":"that make people more human,"},{"time":204000,"text":"and not less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}